item.title: [+950] KFC's Packaging Even Worse Than Its Food
item.description: There are many reasons to avoid dining at Kentucky Fried Chicken for the food alone. A single Extra Crispy Chicken Breast contains 510 calories and 33 g of fat, and the company buys chickens from suppliers who mistreat the birds. But a new report reveals KFC's packaging is even worse, with the company supporting clear-cutting of virgin forests.

item.title: [+507] File-Sharers Safe Until Music Biz Change Laws
item.description: After failing in their case against The Pirate Bay, a music copyrights group has announced it will give up trying to get sites blocked and will leave file-sharers alone. Not forever though. They will instead put all their efforts into getting the law changed. The IFPI said yesterday that it wants to bring this same strategy to your country soon.
